  "remarks": "TAi.067 Title: Maulavi. Designation: a) Deputy Minister of Public Health under the Taliban regime, b) Deputy Minister of Foreign Affairs under the Taliban regime.  Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 29 Jul. 2010. Picture available for inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 January 2001 (amended on 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011, 7 Sep. 2016)",
